<codeline lineno="83"><highlight class="comment">Ubuntu<sp/>packages<sp/>are<sp/>not<sp/>built<sp/>correctly<sp/>at<sp/>least<sp/>on<sp/>64-bit<sp/>platforms.</highlight></codeline>
